OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781251489
OL,3,CCCTV shows moment masked suspect
OL,4,Cfirebombs Imam's house
OL,6,FFootage shows a masked suspect
OL,7,Ffirebombing a home before running away
OL,8,Ffrom the scene.
OL,10,FCCTV has emerged showing the moment a
OL,11,Fmasked suspect firebombed the home of
OL,12,Fan Imam in what is believed to be a
OL,13,F"targeted" attack.
OL,15,FThe footage captures a person, dressed
OL,16,Fin black and wearing a helmet and face
OL,17,Fcovering, smashing the front window of
OL,18,Fthe house in Bolton before hurling a
OL,19,Flit substance inside, triggering a
OL,20,Fmassive fireball.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
