PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781251489
OL,3,CCCTV shows moment masked suspect
OL,4,Cfirebombs Imam's house
OL,6,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,7,Fand all occupants were evacuated with
OL,8,Fno injuries while the fire was
OL,9,Fextinguished.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police confirmed it
OL,12,Fhas launched an arson investigation
OL,13,Fafter the incident which happened
OL,14,Fshorty after 9pm on Wednesday, 10 June.
OL,16,FThe home, on Eastgrove Avenue in the
OL,17,FSharples area of the town, is that of
OL,18,Fa local Imam who lives with his wife
OL,19,Fand children - all of whom were inside
OL,20,Fthe house at the time of the attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
