OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781251489
OL,3,CCCTV shows moment masked suspect
OL,4,Cfirebombs Imam's house
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Mike
OL,7,FSharples said: "Incidents like this
OL,8,Fare not acceptable in our community
OL,9,Fand no one should be made to feel
OL,10,Fthreatened or intimidated.
OL,12,F"Thankfully, no one was injured,
OL,13,Fhowever, the consequences of this
OL,14,Fsuspected arson attack could have been
OL,15,Fvery different.
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
