PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781251489
OL,3,CCCTV shows moment masked suspect
OL,4,Cfirebombs Imam's house
OL,6,F"We understand this incident may cause
OL,7,Fconcern within the community; we are
OL,8,Fworking to find those responsible and
OL,9,Fbring them to justice. We believe this
OL,10,Fwas a targeted attack, and there is no
OL,11,Frisk to the wider public."
OL,13,FHe added: "Our enquiries to identify
OL,14,Fthose responsible are ongoing, and we
OL,15,Furge anyone with information that may
OL,16,Fassist our investigation to please
OL,17,Fcome forward."
OL,19,FIt comes as clashes between police and
OL,20,Frioters continue in Northern Ireland
OL,21,Fover the Belfast knife attack.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
