PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781251489
OL,3,CCCTV shows moment masked suspect
OL,4,Cfirebombs Imam's house
OL,6,FThe suspect, Hadi Alodi, a Sudanese
OL,7,Fnational who was granted leave to
OL,8,Fremain in the UK, allegedly attacked
OL,9,FStephen Ogilvie with a weapon.
OL,11,FStephen's family has reacted to the
OL,12,Fscenes with "disgust" and said the
OL,13,Frioters actions are "not supported by
OL,14,Four family, and peaceful protest is
OL,15,Fonly ever the way forward."
